---
title: Carb Smart Beef and Root Veg Mash Bowl with Peas and Gravy
description: Our tender root veggie mash  – served over top a super savoury beef and delicious gravy – is a beautiful thing. We've included all the flavours of a roasted dinner in a fraction of the time.

Carb Smart (50 g carbohydrates or less) is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.

